8... a5 { Making a square for the Bishop on a6. } 9. Nc3 Bb4 10. Bd2 Ba6 11. a3
Bxc3 12. bxc3 Ne7 13. Ng5 { Making room for the Queen to join the attack. }
13... h6 14. Nh3 Nd7 15. Qg4 g6 16. Nf4
{ White is ready to start sacrificing on e6, while the a6 Bishop is doing nothing. }
