12. g3
{ The best place for the Bishop is on g2 in this position enjoying his time on the long diagonal! }
12... O-O 13. Bg2 a6 14. O-O b5 15. Qh4
{ This is a very typical Queen transfer in this type of positions. } 15... Rfd8
16. a4 { Attacking the over-extended Queen-side. } 16... bxa4 17. Qxa4
{ Was much better for White with the pair of Bishops and presure on Black's Queen-side in the game. }
*

