{ Gave me a free win, making the transition to a winning endgame. 1-0 @@StartBracket@@30@@EndBracket@@ Banzea,A @@StartBracket@@2313@@EndBracket@@ -Polyakov,F @@StartBracket@@2036@@EndBracket@@ Porto Carras 2018 }
