Ned7 12. Nxe6 { Now you can see why we played Qh3! } 12... fxe6 13. Bb2
{ Attacking the Rook. } 13... e5 14. Bxe5 Qe7 15. O-O
{ Getting our King to safety, preparing Re1 if Black takes on e5. } 15... Bg7
16. Bxg7
