16. exd5 { Recapturing the Knight. Notice that the Bishop on b2 is a monster! }
16... Qe3 17. Rde1 { Threatening to move the Bishop, and pin the Queen. } 17...
Qxd3 18. Bxd3+ Kd8 19. Rhf1
{ White will win back the pawn with a much better position due to the strong Bishop on b2, and much more active Rooks. 1-0 @@StartBracket@@23@@EndBracket@@ Golubov,S @@StartBracket@@2484@@EndBracket@@-Tunik,G @@StartBracket@@2378@@EndBracket@@ Taganrog 2018 }
