{ Threatening to take the Bishop at some point. } 17... Qd8 18. Qd6
{ Notice how blocked Black's pieces are! } 18... Ra8 19. Nxc8
{ Finally grabbing the Bishop, because we had no other alternative. } 19...
Qxc8 { Defending b7. } 20. d4 { Opening up the position. } 20... cxd4 21. Qxd4
{ The Bishop is stronger than the Knight in an open position. } *

